contentrichtext.text: '''Wolfenstein''' may refer to: == Geography == * [[Wolfenstein (rock)|Wolfenstein]], a rock formation in Germany == People == * [[Alfred Wolfenstein]] (1888-1945), German poet ([[:de:Alfred Wolfenstein]]) * [[Eugene Victor Wolfenstein]] (1940-2010), distinguished social theorist, practicing psychoanalyst and a professor of Political Science at University of California, Los Angeles * [[Lincoln Wolfenstein]] (b. 1923), American physicist == Video games == * ''[[Wolfenstein (series)]]'', includes: ** ''[[Castle Wolfenstein]]'', a computer game released in 1981 by Muse Software ** ''[[Beyond Castle Wolfenstein]]'', the sequel for the above game, released in 1984 ** ''[[Wolfenstein 3D]]'', a computer game released in 1992 by id Software ** ''[[Spear of Destiny (video game)]]'', the prequel for the above game, released in 1992 ** ''[[Return to Castle Wolfenstein]]'', a computer game released in 2001 ** ''[[Wolfenstein: Enemy Territory]]'', a free multiplayer game based on Return to Castle Wolfenstein, released in 2003 ** ''[[Wolfenstein (2009 video game)]]'', the sequel to 2001's Return to Castle Wolfenstein, released in 2009 by [[Activision]]. ** ''[[Wolfenstein: The New Order]]'' by MachineGames == Movies == * ''[[Return to Castle Wolfenstein (film)]]'', a movie based on the ''Wolfenstein'' series, current production status is unknown. ==See also== * [[Wolfsschanze]] {{disambig}}
